{"tid":2456893,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人經常有dejavu?(既視感）","createTime":"2021-03-22T08:52:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T05:19:44.000Z","uid":277738,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"56cd9840bf9f50eb2112825632820c4bcc42f171","tid":2456893,"uid":277738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T08:52:25.000Z","msg":"//Deja vu是法文的，是由一位法國的神經精神科專家&Eacute;mile Boirac第一次提出這種現象的研究，因此用法文稱呼這種現象為deja vu。大部份的人，偶而或時有一種奇異的經歷或感覺，對自己周圍的景象或是氛圍有熟悉感，好像曾經歷過。//<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n耐唔耐都會有<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但最近發現次數頻密咗好多<br />\n有時會係唔同地點有同一種dejavu<br />\n試過第一次去某個地方<br />\n有個位熟悉到簡直覺得自己曾經處身於嗰度<br />\n<br />\n係咪個腦出咗咩問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b58186f438eca1c10a4a94c788c2c99093aa90","tid":2456893,"uid":277738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T08:52:34.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"f5038a06471394c5b2aefd15cf541ef6e8941231","tid":2456893,"uid":277738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T08:52:48.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"4a0ae303b0e2a3b835000263041959cd6e620ef7","tid":2456893,"uid":36475,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T08:53:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dv13gl0a-FA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fdv13gl0a-FA&d=Hu0SY4Cx1oodln7cCHpxba0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=7e114060\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dv13gl0a-FA</a>"},{"pid":"63b03a335769685add97c7c33f387bd35f56ba7d","tid":2456893,"uid":277738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T08:54:09.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"4005e57e81e02ad85beb9e91bef06f8eeda6b7ed","tid":2456893,"uid":376290,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4a0ae303b0e2a3b835000263041959cd6e620ef7","tid":2456893,"uid":36475,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T08:53:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dv13gl0a-FA